title: MQM’s Asiya Ishaq Siddiquee wins NA-232 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Mutahida Qaumi Movement (MQM)’ Pakistan Candidate Asiya Ishaq Siddiquee has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-232 Korangi-I by securing 88,260 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Adeel Ahmed, who bagged 66,576 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 43.60 percent.
